title: Ep 485 If the Dems Win Today the Impeachment Talk Will Explode
description:
In this episode I cover why Trump cannot be indicted. A sitting POTUS' power is checked by a political, not a criminal process. https://www.conservativereview.com/articles/levin-trump-cannot-be-indicted-say-doj-memoranda   I also address a pending Supreme Court case that could have a profound effect on upcoming elections.
